1177
01:21:43,471 --> 01:21:44,699
<i>Anna.</i>

1178
01:21:47,108 --> 01:21:48,598
Anna?

1179
01:21:49,410 --> 01:21:52,379
My name's Michael Clayton.
I'm a friend of Arthur's.

1180
