1319
01:35:42,914 --> 01:35:44,643
Take it easy, Gabe.

1320
01:35:45,650 --> 01:35:47,015
Michael.

1321
01:35:58,764 --> 01:36:00,197
<i>Check.</i>

1322
01:36:02,034 --> 01:36:03,296
<i>Check.</i>

1323
01:36:03,636 --> 01:36:06,366
